# <%= projectName %>

A Slidev presentation project powered by [slidev-ppt-agent](https://github.com/Rory-X/slidev-ppt-agent).

## Quick Start

Open this project in your AI agent (Cursor, Claude Code, Codex, etc.) and say:

```
/ppt-creator 帮我做一个关于 xxx 的技术分享 PPT
```

The agent handles everything: research, style, outline, composition, preview, and publishing.

## Commands

| Command | Description |
|---------|-------------|
| `/ppt-creator <requirement>` | Full pipeline: research -> style -> outline -> compose -> preview |
| `/ppt-review [slides-file]` | Quality review with auto-fix |
| `/ppt-publish [vercel\|github-pages]` | Deploy to static hosting |

## Manual Usage

```bash
# Preview a slides file
npx slidev slides-topic.md

# Build static site
npx slidev build slides-topic.md --out dist

# Local static preview
node scripts/static-preview-server.js --dir=dist --port=3045
```

## Project Structure

```
├── .agents/skills/       # Agent skills (research, design, outline, compose, etc.)
├── design-system/        # Tokens, archetypes, page templates, CSS
├── schemas/              # JSON Schema validation
├── scripts/              # Engineering helpers
├── artifacts/            # Generated intermediate files
├── AGENTS.md             # Universal agent entry point
└── slides-*.md           # Your presentations
```

